{"tid":1782640,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店系列 灣仔 麵匠風龍","createTime":"2019-12-14T06:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T07:57:19.000Z","uid":166062,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de47451b82d29cf6fd4773aeda081420c0be573c","tid":1782640,"uid":166062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F3oHA1i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF3oHA1i.jpg&h=e7ad8132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nbr2A1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbr2A1k.jpg&h=ccf790e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3QfbzG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3QfbzG.jpg&h=8a650c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJFF672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJFF672.jpg&h=2b26237f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DzJXpUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzJXpUJ.jpg&h=e3f8eae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfaOwzK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfaOwzK.jpg&h=8222d775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2c1RCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2c1RCu.jpg&h=31fc4733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n價錢同別天神好似 都係105蚊套餐平5蚊 <br />\n餃子/沙律 我都係食番沙律 <br />\n沙律差唔多 麵真係好食d <br />\n今次唔洗自己再落調味<br />\n個豬肉係幾好食 但唔係叉燒係豬扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完之後呆左 唸緊叉燒係咁既味咩 <br />\n本身見佢幾厚身仲開心左下 上個時個肉勁香<br />\n多人食到要排隊 單丁都成10分鐘<br />\n店員都係黃既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a37330a69138caa25bd4a548936a15d111c6a72","tid":1782640,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:50:56.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25